<?xml version="1.0"?><speak version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis" xml:lang="zh-CN"><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">【朗诵稿：霜月寄相思】</prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">（轻柔舒缓地）</prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">各位朋友，今夜让我们穿越回一千三百年前的长安城郊。<break strength="medium"/>烛火摇曳的客栈里，有位青衫落拓的诗人正辗转难眠。<break strength="medium"/>他叫李白，此时不过二十六岁，却已离家漂泊三载有余。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">（稍顿，<break strength="medium"/>语调清亮）</prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">请听这四句千古绝唱：</prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">&quot;床前明月光，<break strength="medium"/>疑是地上霜。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">举头望明月，<break strength="medium"/>低头思故乡。<break strength="medium"/>&quot;</prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">（转为温厚解说）</prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">月光如银绸铺满雕花木榻，恍惚间竟似深秋寒霜。<break strength="medium"/>这神来之比的背后，藏着盛唐特有的浪漫气象——彼时多少文人跨州越县追寻抱负，李青莲的蜀道行囊里，既装着&quot;天生我材必有用&quot;的豪情，也压着&quot;何时到粟里&quot;的乡愁。<break strength="medium"/>看似直白的二十字，恰似水墨点染出永恒的中秋意象。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">（叙事节奏渐起）</prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">您可曾见过长安的秋夜？<break strength="medium"/>寒蛩声里，竹帘轻晃，霜白的月光漫过窗棂，在游子的衾被上勾画出梧桐树影。<break strength="medium"/>他忽然翻身坐起，锦靴踩在如水月华里，凉意自脚底漫上心头。<break strength="medium"/>推窗的刹那，玉盘似的明月正悬在朱雀大街的飞檐间，像极了他离家那晚峨眉山巅的月亮。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">（情感渐浓，<break strength="medium"/>语速放缓）</prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">手指无意识抚过随身携带的桃木梳——那是临行前妹妹塞进行囊的。<break strength="medium"/>巴蜀的桂香，剑南的茶韵，忽然在喉间泛起微微的苦涩。<break strength="medium"/>他想起老父灯下教他念《子虚赋》的咳嗽声，阿母总在重阳蒸的菊花糕，此刻都化作了砚台中渐渐凝固的墨。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">（深情收尾）</prosody><break strength="medium"/><prosody rate="medium" pitch="medium">千年后的我们依然看见，那袭青衫如何在对月成三人时，落下这滴最清澈的乡愁。<break strength="medium"/>正如琥珀封存松脂，这首小诗永远定格了华夏儿女心中最温柔的羁绊——走得再远，总有一片月光，永远照着回家的路。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="medium"/></speak>